bio: Hello! I'm Sareen Garnaik, a passionate Software Developer specializing in full-stack development. With over three years of experience in building web applications, I have honed my skills in JavaScript, React, Node, MongoDB, solidity etc. Currently, I am working as a Senior Developer at Tech Innovations, where I lead a team in developing scalable and user-friendly applications. I have successfully delivered numerous projects, including an e-commerce platform that increased the client's sales by 30%. I hold a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science from Stanford University. My key strengths include problem-solving, project management, and a keen eye for detail. I am also proficient in cloud technologies and DevOps practices. Outside of work, I enjoy hiking, photography, and exploring new technologies. My goal is to continue growing as a developer and eventually transition into a leadership role where I can mentor and guide the next generation of tech enthusiasts.
